cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual tracking and proposes a new formulation of the constellation model with correlation filters. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a novel color model and proposes a highly efficient optimization for MAP inference of a fully-connected constellation. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with modeling objects at different levels of detail and proposes a tracker that uses deformable parts models. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with visual tracking and proposes a new approach using correlation filters. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with object localization and tracking, which are important tasks in robotics.
